You think a big boss like him

291
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:00,960
would live in some suburban rental,

292
00:17:01,510 --> 00:17:02,630
cramming on a packed bus for over an hour

293
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:04,230
every day just to get to work?

294
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:13,480
Chao, he's here.

295
00:17:15,829 --> 00:17:16,829
Let's see if he turns on the left

296
00:17:16,829 --> 00:17:17,960
or right turn signal.

297
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:18,640
He's signaling.

298
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:19,569
He's signaling.

299
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,330
He took the highway.

300
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:38,000
I've thought it through for you.

301
00:17:38,550 --> 00:17:40,790
You should take the bronze bianzhong set,

302
00:17:40,790 --> 00:17:41,990
not that lousy plate.

303
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:43,400
Why?

304
00:17:45,110 --> 00:17:46,160
The bianzhong set,

305
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:48,280
43.8 million.

306
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:50,660
That lousy plate is only 20 million.

307
00:17:50,790 --> 00:17:51,880
That's a difference of

308
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:53,490
23.8 million.

309
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:54,790
Besides,

310
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:56,920
a set of bianzhong has real presence.

311
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:59,380
Imagine the statement they make
on display.

312
00:18:00,050 --> 00:18:02,250
Exactly because they're too imposing,

313
00:18:02,350 --> 00:18:04,280
I wouldn't even dare display them.

314
00:18:05,750 --> 00:18:07,610
It's right for others to think so,

315
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:09,770
but you don't need to worry about that.

316
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:10,640
Why?

317
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:14,010
You're on the first floor.

318
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:16,270
You can dig a basement.

319
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:18,880
By then, forget the bianzhong set—

320
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:20,320
even the Houmuwu Ding

321
00:18:20,510 --> 00:18:21,710
could fit down there.

322
00:18:22,550 --> 00:18:23,590
Dig a basement?

323
00:18:24,830 --> 00:18:25,790
Our company

324
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,780
will do it for you—free.

325
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:28,480
Well.

326
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,370
I even brought the blueprints.

327
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:32,610
Please take a look.

328
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,320
Waterproof,

329
00:18:36,520 --> 00:18:37,230
shockproof,

330
00:18:36,650 --> 00:18:36,740
[Home Design Construction Drawings]

331
00:18:37,350 --> 00:18:38,800
[Drawing Index] [Project Overview]

332
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:38,030
theft-proof,

333
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:38,720
and nuclear blast-proof—

334
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:40,580
you can rest completely assured.

335
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:45,910
[Fang Zhong Zhuang Shi Gong Cheng You Xian Gong Si]
[Home Design Construction Drawings]

336
00:18:46,870 --> 00:18:48,270
That's too much trouble.

337
00:18:49,030 --> 00:18:50,830
I'll just take the Ru ware plate.

338
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:00,800
Mr. Fang,

339
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,830
do you know

340
00:19:02,850 --> 00:19:04,380
the story behind the plate?

341
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,710
This plate

342
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:08,240
was specially commissioned
by Emperor Qinzong of Song

343
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:10,100
for his father, Emperor Huizong.

344
00:19:10,590 --> 00:19:11,510
And the very next day

345
00:19:11,510 --> 00:19:12,680
after father and son saw it—

346
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,590
guess what?

347
00:19:14,110 --> 00:19:17,070
The Jin army stormed Kaifeng.

348
00:19:18,750 --> 00:19:19,410
After that,

349
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:22,050
the three successive owners of this plate

350
00:19:22,510 --> 00:19:24,560
were killed one after another,

351
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:27,160
as if cursed.

352
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:29,920
Even those who tried to obtain it

353
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,610
met bad ends.

354
00:19:32,470 --> 00:19:33,240
This time,

355
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,920
after it was salvaged,

356
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:37,960
the previous buyer

357
00:19:38,030 --> 00:19:39,960
had just made full payment—

358
00:19:40,070 --> 00:19:42,130
and before he even got to see it, he...

359
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:03,960
Right now, we've got

360
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:05,360
both of these things.

361
00:20:06,030 --> 00:20:07,090
Which one to choose

362
00:20:07,270 --> 00:20:08,110
is up to you.

363
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:14,610
I've made up my mind.

364
00:20:15,830 --> 00:20:17,110
And your choice is?

365
00:20:19,070 --> 00:20:20,260
The Ru ware plate.

366
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:23,760
Mr. Fang, you...

367
00:20:26,270 --> 00:20:27,160
Just kidding.

368
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,770
I've made up my mind.

369
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:33,120
I want the bianzhong set.

370
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:35,200
Wise.

371
00:20:40,750 --> 00:20:41,270
Uncle!

372
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:44,990
We can't hand it to each other directly.

373
00:20:45,550 --> 00:20:46,550
It's just bronze!

374
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,330
How much do you want?

375
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:00,460
2.5 million.

376
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:01,370
Vulgar!

377
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,510
Petty!

378
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:04,680
I offer 800,000.

379
00:21:05,790 --> 00:21:06,400
800,000...

380
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,550
Uncle Fei doing business with you

381
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:09,150
is already doing you a favor.

382
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,140
Don't push your luck.

383
00:21:16,310 --> 00:21:17,310
A-Alright.

384
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:19,310
Then...

385
00:21:19,830 --> 00:21:21,230
when can we make the deal?

386
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:23,650
We can do it now.

387
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:27,260
Where's the money?

388
00:21:27,310 --> 00:21:27,880
What?

389
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:31,330
Are you afraid Uncle Fei will rip you off?

390
00:21:35,240 --> 00:21:36,300
I have a condition.

391
00:21:37,350 --> 00:21:38,350
When this is sold,

392
00:21:38,830 --> 00:21:40,160
I'll give you the money.

393
00:21:42,270 --> 00:21:43,330
If you're worried,

394
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:44,500
you can take

395
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:46,100
this small one back first.

396
00:21:46,240 --> 00:21:47,400
When we sell it,

397
00:21:47,550 --> 00:21:48,350
you give it to me.

398
00:21:48,350 --> 00:21:49,080
Is that okay?

399
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,360
To be honest,

400
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:56,070
my buyer won't accept anything

401
00:21:56,070 --> 00:21:57,920
that isn't a complete set.

402
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:03,860
A-Alright.

403
00:22:04,510 --> 00:22:05,760
Call the buyer.

404
00:22:06,270 --> 00:22:07,730
Within the next day or two,

405
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:10,000
we'll go to Sanjiangkou together.

406
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:10,440
Uncle,

407
00:22:10,750 --> 00:22:12,150
I won't be going with you.

408
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,030
Why?

409
00:22:16,030 --> 00:22:17,030
To be honest,

410
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:19,530
I'm in trouble with the law.

411
00:22:20,070 --> 00:22:21,510
With things this high-profile,

412
00:22:21,510 --> 00:22:22,370
I don't dare to.

413
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,110
Well, then,

414
00:22:23,110 --> 00:22:24,770
how are you going to get there?

415
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:25,960
The buyer is waiting.

416
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:26,590
Besides,

417
00:22:26,590 --> 00:22:28,400
I am a very punctual person.

418
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:29,000
Uncle,

419
00:22:30,070 --> 00:22:31,270
don't worry about me.

420
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:33,810
I'll figure it out myself.

421
00:22:34,830 --> 00:22:36,160
See you in Sanjiangkou.

422
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:05,680
It might be evidence.

423
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:08,880
Most likely connected to Lu Zheng's death.

424
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:11,720
This thing

425
00:23:11,750 --> 00:23:13,950
can never show up in Sanjiangkou again.

426
00:23:37,830 --> 00:23:39,230
It's still running fine.

427
00:23:55,790 --> 00:23:56,350
Zhou Qi!

428
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,480
Officers,

429
00:24:07,510 --> 00:24:08,780
why are you here?

430
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:11,440
That's quite an outfit you're wearing.

431
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:15,150
Where did you go?

432
00:24:18,070 --> 00:24:18,830
I went out

433
00:24:19,030 --> 00:24:19,960
with my friends.

434
00:24:31,790 --> 00:24:33,240
The person who sold me these things

435
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:34,300
is Zheng Yongbing.

436
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:36,200
He deals in antiques

437
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:38,720
and is a regular at our place.

438
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:40,310
He once tipped a waitress

439
00:24:40,310 --> 00:24:42,240
with a gold necklace.

440
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,830
She had it appraised,

441
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:47,730
and it turned out to be real.

442
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:48,720
He told us

443
00:24:48,750 --> 00:24:50,400
that he had a lot of jewelry

444
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:53,130
and could sell it to us cheaply.

445
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:55,110
He said even Mr. Zhou Rong

446
00:24:55,510 --> 00:24:56,850
bought things from him.

447
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,400
So I believed him.

448
00:25:00,210 --> 00:25:01,870
I bought a necklace,

449
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,350
a bracelet,

450
00:25:04,110 --> 00:25:05,630
two rings,

451
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:07,690
and a pair of earrings from him.

452
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:10,330
All for 20,000 yuan.

453
00:25:13,460 --> 00:25:14,230
On the night

454
00:25:15,070 --> 00:25:16,330
of Ye Jian's incident,

455
00:25:16,350 --> 00:25:17,680
were you at Fenglinwan?

456
00:25:17,790 --> 00:25:18,440
Yes.

457
00:25:18,660 --> 00:25:19,960
Between 11 p.m.

458
00:25:19,980 --> 00:25:21,380
and midnight that night,

459
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:23,210
who can confirm you were there?

460
00:25:25,110 --> 00:25:27,110
Between 11 p.m. and midnight...

461
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:32,080
Are you suspecting that I...

462
00:25:33,270 --> 00:25:34,010
Oh my God.

463
00:25:34,110 --> 00:25:35,200
I-I'm just a woman.

464
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:36,160
How could I possibly kill someone?

465
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,220
Who can confirm it?

466
00:25:37,790 --> 00:25:38,960
Everyone at Fenglinwan

467
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:40,070
can confirm it.

468
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:43,720
That night, I was at the bar downstairs
the whole time.

469
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,110
We had

470
00:25:45,110 --> 00:25:47,070
an internet-famous DJ playing there.

471
00:25:47,070 --> 00:25:48,400
I was there all evening.

472
00:25:52,270 --> 00:25:52,790
Qi,

473
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:53,880
so they only brought you in
for questioning

474
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:54,960
because of the stolen goods

475
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:55,790
you bought

476
00:25:56,350 --> 00:25:57,790
from Zheng Yongbing?

477
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:03,460
I don't think that's the only reason.

478
00:26:04,240 --> 00:26:06,900
The police might just be
using that as an excuse.

479
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,110
Oh, right,

480
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:12,590
they also asked me about Ye Jian.

481
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:17,860
What about that watch?
Did they ask about it?

482
00:26:18,350 --> 00:26:19,440
Yibo, don't worry.

483
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:21,750
I got rid of that watch myself.

484
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:23,830
By now it should be on a train,

485
00:26:23,830 --> 00:26:25,360
far away from Sanjiangkou.

486
00:26:27,270 --> 00:26:27,920
Qi.

487
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:31,770
Everything that's been happening lately

488
00:26:32,030 --> 00:26:33,430
has been way too intense.

489
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:35,530
Yeah, way too intense.

490
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:38,640
When I went into the police station,

491
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:39,550
I was so nervous

492
00:26:39,550 --> 00:26:40,680
I almost passed out.

493
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:42,640
I thought the police were going

494
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,900
to catch us right then.

495
00:26:46,690 --> 00:26:48,070
Feel my chest.

496
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,460
My heart is still pounding.

497
00:26:52,270 --> 00:26:54,000
My heart is pounding too.

498
00:26:59,110 --> 00:26:59,720
Yibo...

499
00:27:01,830 --> 00:27:03,160
I'm feeling something.

500
00:27:06,430 --> 00:27:07,430
Seems like it.

501
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:16,200
Yibo,

502
00:27:17,070 --> 00:27:18,530
you're getting worked up.

503
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:21,740
Danger and excitement

504
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:23,590
are your turn-ons.

505
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:26,400
Then...

506
00:27:27,070 --> 00:27:28,870
say something else to excite me.

507
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:32,110
Like what?

508
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:33,830
Like what?

509
00:27:35,070 --> 00:27:36,550
Whatever's thrilling.

510
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:40,160
The police are about to find that watch.

511
00:27:41,070 --> 00:27:41,830
What else?

512
00:27:42,750 --> 00:27:45,030
Mr. Rong won't let us off.

513
00:27:50,550 --> 00:27:52,810
Your game account's about to get hacked!

514
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,330
At the explosion scene,

515
00:27:58,440 --> 00:28:00,590
Lu Yibo intercepted the report letter.

516
00:28:00,590 --> 00:28:01,460
Meanwhile,

517
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:03,550
a jewelry store
in the provincial capital was robbed.

518
00:28:03,550 --> 00:28:04,640
The stolen goods

519
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,400
were transferred to Sanjiangkou

520
00:28:06,400 --> 00:28:09,310
and ended up
in the hands of this man, Zheng Yongbing.

521
00:28:09,310 --> 00:28:11,030
Zheng Yongbing then sold them

522
00:28:11,070 --> 00:28:12,410
to Zhou Qi.

523
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:16,400
Zhou Qi is Lu Yibo's girlfriend.

524
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:17,610
How does this

525
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:19,680
connect back to the provincial capital
explosion case again?

526
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:20,510
I see it now.

527
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:22,110
They're a gang, right?

528
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,070
Zheng Yongbing is in charge of
fencing the stolen goods.

529
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:25,200
You see what? What do you see?

530
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:26,240
How could Zheng Yongbing

531
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:28,170
possibly be connected to the case?

532
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:37,110
Chief Zhang,

533
00:28:37,110 --> 00:28:37,690
I think

534
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:38,780
he has nothing to do

535
00:28:38,790 --> 00:28:39,850
with our case here.

536
00:28:41,230 --> 00:28:41,820
Oh!

537
00:28:44,070 --> 00:28:45,100
Didn't he say

538
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:47,910
that even Zhou Rong
bought things from him too?

539
00:28:47,960 --> 00:28:49,690
I think we should look into him.

540
00:28:51,950 --> 00:28:54,610
It's necessary to
investigate Zheng Yongbing.

541
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:55,370
Chief Zhang,

542
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:56,000
I think,

543
00:28:56,020 --> 00:28:57,270
since it's related to
a provincial capital case,

544
00:28:57,270 --> 00:28:58,220
we should report it up

545
00:28:58,220 --> 00:28:59,480
and let them handle it.

546
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:01,350
If this case is going to be investigated,

547
00:29:01,350 --> 00:29:03,440
we'll have to handle it ourselves.

548
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:04,690
Chief Zhang,

549
00:29:04,780 --> 00:29:05,960
I know you're capable.

550
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:07,070
You can solve any case;

551
00:29:07,070 --> 00:29:08,000
it's just a matter of time,

552
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:08,480
right?

553
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:10,880
But we have to prioritize.

554
00:29:11,070 --> 00:29:11,830
Ye's case,

555
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:12,830
my mentor's case—

556
00:29:12,830 --> 00:29:13,830
we don't even have leads yet.

557
00:29:13,830 --> 00:29:14,400
And there're tons of customers

558
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,590
at Fenglinwan worth investigating.

559
00:29:15,590 --> 00:29:16,830
Can we really go through them one by one?

560
00:29:16,830 --> 00:29:17,640
If necessary,

561
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:20,030
then yes—

562
00:29:20,490 --> 00:29:22,350
we have to investigate them one by one.

563
00:29:22,350 --> 00:29:23,510
I agree.

564
00:29:24,790 --> 00:29:25,790
And we need to look into

565
00:29:25,790 --> 00:29:27,030
that internet-famous DJ too,

566
00:29:27,030 --> 00:29:29,360
to verify
if Zhou Qi was telling the truth.

567
00:29:30,310 --> 00:29:30,880
I agree.

568
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:31,790
Okay.

569
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,330
If everyone agrees,

570
00:29:34,510 --> 00:29:35,370
we'll start...

571
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:38,000
Captain Wang, what do you think?

572
00:29:38,550 --> 00:29:39,960
I think...

573
00:29:42,590 --> 00:29:43,160
I agree.

574
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:44,200
Good.

575
00:29:44,630 --> 00:29:45,960
Since everyone agrees,

576
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:48,440
we'll investigate Zheng Yongbing.

577
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:02,480
Zheng,

578
00:30:02,840 --> 00:30:03,470
have you eaten?

579
00:30:03,470 --> 00:30:05,200
Just heading out for lunch now.

580
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:30,600
Zheng Yongbing,

581
00:30:30,820 --> 00:30:31,810
46 years old.

582
00:30:32,550 --> 00:30:33,680
At 17, he was sentenced to three years

583
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:34,480
for theft.

584
00:30:34,750 --> 00:30:35,700
At 23,

585
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:38,240
sentenced to five years for tomb raiding.

586
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:38,960
After release,

587
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,510
no further offenses on record.

588
00:30:40,510 --> 00:30:42,300
He now runs an antique shop.

589
00:30:43,270 --> 00:30:43,830
Zheng!

590
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:47,020
Eat up, eat up.

591
00:30:47,040 --> 00:30:47,900
I'll go line up.

592
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:49,880
Family-wise,

593
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,480
he divorced his wife years ago.

594
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:52,960
Their child lives with her.

595
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:55,000
Captain Wang learned from some insiders

596
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:55,960
that, besides

597
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:57,440
his antique shop business,

598
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:58,500
he also secretly deals in stolen goods

599
00:30:58,500 --> 00:30:59,720
and resells cultural relics.

600
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:00,320
But so far,

601
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:02,800
these have all been small-scale dealings.

602
00:31:03,280 --> 00:31:05,000
There might be something bigger

603
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:07,060
hiding behind those small dealings.

604
00:31:25,580 --> 00:31:28,640
[Antique and Modern Collectibles;
Jade and Precious Stones]

605
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:33,250
Can we see him from here?

606
00:31:40,170 --> 00:31:42,660
[Antique and Modern Collectibles;
Jade and Precious Stones]

607
00:31:42,730 --> 00:31:44,260
What's he eating for lunch?

608
00:31:51,150 --> 00:31:52,480
You've even got the equipment?

609
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:53,510
Good. Not bad.

610
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,560
He's eating pretty lightly.

611
00:31:58,640 --> 00:31:59,440
Cornbread,

612
00:31:59,590 --> 00:32:00,720
boiled vegetables.

613
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:02,030
He has fatty liver disease.

614
00:32:02,030 --> 00:32:03,960
His doctor told him to lose weight.

615
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:05,790
Then that diet's on point.

616
00:32:05,790 --> 00:32:07,850
Cornbread is made from whole grains.

617
00:32:08,510 --> 00:32:09,840
He's quite enjoying it.

618
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:12,750
Chief,

619
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:14,130
are you hungry?

620
00:32:15,750 --> 00:32:16,510
I'm fine.

621
00:32:19,270 --> 00:32:21,270
I brought two buns from the canteen.

622
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:24,010
Pickled cabbage filling.

623
00:32:25,270 --> 00:32:27,130
Buns... Y-You even brought buns?

624
00:32:27,350 --> 00:32:28,750
Is your bag a magic bag or something?

625
00:32:28,750 --> 00:32:29,550
I'll have one.

626
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,290
Some people live to eat.

627
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,030
And I eat to live.

628
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:49,020
Go ahead, say what you want to say.

629
00:32:50,590 --> 00:32:52,680
I feel like you've been very confident

630
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:53,810
these past few days.

631
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:55,000
Yeah?

632
00:32:57,030 --> 00:32:57,510
What's that supposed to mean?

633
00:32:57,510 --> 00:32:59,040
I wasn't confident before?

634
00:32:59,110 --> 00:33:00,440
That's not what I meant.

635
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:03,510
It's true. I...

636
00:33:06,030 --> 00:33:06,720
Over the years,

637
00:33:06,720 --> 00:33:08,790
I haven't liked to
get involved in these things much.

638
00:33:08,790 --> 00:33:09,640
Mainly because

639
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:10,590
for a long stretch,

640
00:33:10,590 --> 00:33:12,480
I was just... jinxed.

641
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:14,850
Whenever I got involved,

642
00:33:15,310 --> 00:33:16,200
not only could I not help,

643
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:18,530
but I'd end up causing trouble for others.

644
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,170
But

645
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:19,920
I found that

646
00:33:20,070 --> 00:33:21,640
since I came to Sanjiangkou,

647
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:23,030
something's different.

648
00:33:23,030 --> 00:33:24,360
Something has changed.

649
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:25,130
It's like...

650
00:33:27,030 --> 00:33:28,000
my bad luck has turned to good fortune,

651
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:30,000
and every disaster into a blessing.

652
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,000
I've decided.

653
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:36,480
From now on,

654
00:33:37,480 --> 00:33:38,610
I'm going to change.

655
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:39,830
I have to...

656
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:41,240
I have to...

657
00:33:41,440 --> 00:33:43,040
Show off your skills, Chief.

658
00:33:47,110 --> 00:33:48,440
Can I ask you something?

659
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:50,030
Chief, please go ahead.

660
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:50,720
Just that.

661
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:52,200
When it's

662
00:33:52,310 --> 00:33:53,320
just the two of us

663
00:33:53,350 --> 00:33:54,330
in the future,

664
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:56,540
stop calling me "Chief" all the time.

665
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:57,980
Just call me Zhang.

666
00:34:02,030 --> 00:34:03,550
Okay. Zhang.

667
00:34:23,210 --> 00:34:27,199
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]

668
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,230
I already spoke on the phone

669
00:34:36,230 --> 00:34:36,960
with that out-of-town

670
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:38,159
internet-famous DJ.

671
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:39,510
They said that night,

672
00:34:39,510 --> 00:34:40,679
Zhou Qi really was around

673
00:34:40,679 --> 00:34:41,840
the DJ booth at Fenglinwan the whole time,

674
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,969
looking after them.

675
00:34:43,670 --> 00:34:44,500
So we're just supposed to

676
00:34:44,500 --> 00:34:45,360
take his word for it?

677
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:47,090
Besides, he's not even in town.

678
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:57,430
What's wrong?

679
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:00,670
Since he's an internet-famous DJ

680
00:35:00,670 --> 00:35:02,110
performing at Fenglinwan,

681
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:04,370
there should be some buzz online, right?

682
00:35:12,430 --> 00:35:20,260
[Chuanshi Antique Collections]

683
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,660
Next time, don't just bring buns.

684
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:17,490
Bring some vinegar,

685
00:35:17,670 --> 00:35:18,360
garlic,

686
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:19,960
and chili.

687
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:21,960
We can't just swallow them dry either.

688
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:23,580
Better to have something to drink, right?

689
00:35:23,580 --> 00:35:25,400
Some porridge would be even better.

690
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:29,940
♪ Throw a toy to
that bunch of brokers in town ♪

691
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:27,920
Zheng!

692
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:28,670
Hey, man!

693
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:29,800
How are you? Have you eaten?

694
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:30,890
Not yet. Going back to eat.

695
00:35:30,890 --> 00:35:31,950
-See you.
-See you.

696
00:35:33,890 --> 00:35:37,730
♪ From doubt, I forge a weapon ♪

697
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:36,320
Zhang.

698
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:37,880
Zheng Yongbing really

699
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,680
doesn't look suspicious at all.

700
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:41,320
That's

701
00:35:41,270 --> 00:35:42,650
♪ Oh, god ♪

702
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:42,360
exactly the point.

703
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:43,480
The fact that he looks so unsuspicious

704
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:44,670
is precisely what makes him suspicious.

705
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:46,900
♪ Please give me some guidance ♪

706
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:50,160
He used to fight a lot when he was young

707
00:35:48,370 --> 00:35:50,950
♪ Find the sleepy poet ♪

708
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:51,440
and did some time.

709
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:53,120
Now he's got a bit of money.

710
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:54,260
♪ They are all guests ♪

711
00:35:55,190 --> 00:35:55,850
Look at him.

712
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,110
Don't you think he's being a bit

713
00:35:57,110 --> 00:35:58,150
too low-key?

714
00:35:58,970 --> 00:36:01,510
♪ There's a strange, hazy feeling ♪

715
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:00,690
What is he hiding

716
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:02,820
that he's so afraid of being noticed?

717
00:36:03,050 --> 00:36:04,400
♪ Waiting for me to make sense of it ♪

718
00:36:05,080 --> 00:36:07,330
♪ Worshippers hiding in the smoke,
just beyond reach ♪

719
00:36:08,580 --> 00:36:10,840
What's he doing
wandering around like that?

720
00:36:09,510 --> 00:36:10,920
♪ They are all guests ♪

721
00:36:14,130 --> 00:36:15,620
♪ Be patient and wait ♪

722
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:23,840
♪ Be patient and wait ♪

723
00:36:27,070 --> 00:36:28,340
♪ Be patient and wait ♪

724
00:36:28,510 --> 00:36:29,230
Look.

725
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:32,540
He's definitely got something going on.

726
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:41,760
Sir!

727
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:42,280
What's wrong?

728
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:43,360
Don't park at the entrance!

729
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:44,250
Move it up.

730
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,810
I can park on the side, yeah?

731
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:04,480
Zhang!

732
00:37:04,690 --> 00:37:05,690
Stop right there!

733
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:06,730
W-What's wrong?

734
00:37:07,230 --> 00:37:08,430
Let me see your phone.

735
00:37:08,510 --> 00:37:09,480
Why do you want to see my phone?

736
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:10,590
Who were you calling behind my back?

737
00:37:10,590 --> 00:37:11,440
I didn't call anyone!

738
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:12,670
-I wasn't doing anything...
-Give it to me!

739
00:37:12,670 --> 00:37:13,480
Look, I just...

740
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:14,630
I just called my colleague Tian.

741
00:37:14,630 --> 00:37:14,960
You...

742
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:16,290
Right, your colleague!

743
00:37:20,670 --> 00:37:21,270
He's gone.

744
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:24,160
He must've just come out to buy dinner.

745
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:25,800
Look.

746
00:37:26,190 --> 00:37:26,720
Let's go.

747
00:37:28,110 --> 00:37:28,630
Zhang.

748
00:37:45,440 --> 00:37:46,840
You're munching away quite happily there.

749
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:48,240
Are you looking closely?

750
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:49,800
My mouth may not have stopped,

751
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,660
but my eyes never left the screen.

752
00:37:53,440 --> 00:37:55,300
Captain Wang, have some nuts too.

753
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:01,380
Thousands of photos here.

754
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:04,370
When are we ever going to
get through them all?

755
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:05,840
Seriously.

756
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:07,030
You've checked my phone
three times this week.

757
00:38:07,030 --> 00:38:08,030
Can't you trust me a little?

758
00:38:08,030 --> 00:38:09,280
Do you really think
I'd do something like that to you?

759
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:09,680
You...

760
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:10,800
You haven't?

761
00:38:11,320 --> 00:38:12,420
Well, let me see.

762
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:13,150
Go ahead.

763
00:38:13,150 --> 00:38:14,000
It's all work stuff!

764
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:14,860
What could I...

765
00:38:15,150 --> 00:38:16,300
I'd like to see

766
00:38:17,030 --> 00:38:18,630
what kind of work business
you've got going on.

767
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:19,340
Check then.

768
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:21,640
You're not gonna find anything anyway.

769
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:23,670
What did you find?

770
00:38:26,710 --> 00:38:27,570
He went inside.

771
00:38:29,550 --> 00:38:32,150
Acting all jumpy—
he's definitely hiding something.

772
00:38:32,150 --> 00:38:32,750
Should we

773
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:33,760
follow him in?

774
00:38:34,190 --> 00:38:34,670
Okay.

775
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:39,510
A call.

776
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:43,190
Chief Zhang, a major discovery.

777
00:38:43,190 --> 00:38:44,150
Ye was at Fenglinwan

778
00:38:44,150 --> 00:38:45,000
that night.

779
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:47,280
See?

780
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,240
Okay, I'll be right back.

781
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:50,960
Should I go back with you?

782
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:51,840
No, no.

783
00:38:51,930 --> 00:38:53,550
You stay here and keep watching.

784
00:38:53,550 --> 00:38:54,630
Something's off about that guy.

785
00:38:54,630 --> 00:38:56,070
Something's definitely going on.

786
00:38:56,070 --> 00:38:57,730
I'll let Song Xing replace me.

787
00:38:58,720 --> 00:38:59,910
[Loyalty]

788
00:39:00,500 --> 00:39:01,390
[Loyalty]

789
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:06,070
Which one is he?

790
00:39:06,070 --> 00:39:06,600
This one.

791
00:39:09,670 --> 00:39:10,730
This is Captain Ye?

792
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:11,300
That...

793
00:39:11,550 --> 00:39:12,810
That's definitely Ye.

794
00:39:13,150 --> 00:39:14,400
That hairstyle, that build—

795
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:16,860
it's like he's standing
right in front of me.

796
00:39:18,630 --> 00:39:19,590
If we just take this blurry photo

797
00:39:19,590 --> 00:39:21,000
of the back of his head

798
00:39:21,070 --> 00:39:21,920
to Fenglinwan,

799
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:22,880
it won't be appropriate, right?

800
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:24,480
We just brought Zhou Qi in

801
00:39:24,630 --> 00:39:26,480
to assist with the investigation.

802
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:28,340
Lu Yibo is on high alert right now.

803
00:39:28,470 --> 00:39:29,480
He would just deny everything.

804
00:39:29,480 --> 00:39:30,880
This photo won't help us.

805
00:39:32,230 --> 00:39:33,700
So you're saying
the lead isn't strong enough?

806
00:39:33,700 --> 00:39:35,830
This doesn't even count as a real lead.

807
00:39:36,110 --> 00:39:37,150
Are there

808
00:39:37,190 --> 00:39:37,800
any clearer photos?

809
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:38,860
I'll keep looking.

810
00:39:49,230 --> 00:39:50,710
Should we bring in some more manpower?
